Greetings from the Media Club,
                                             Do you guys go bonkers about
direction, script writing,cinematography and action? Then, here's a chance
to participate in the Saarang's Short Film Contest.
                                            We, the Media Club are going to
shoot a Short Film in the month of December which will be sent to compete
in the Saarang's Short film contest as well as the other college's fests.
For this to happen we need people who are frenzy about action and
direction. In order to pick out the best ones we are going to conduct an
Audition on November 3rd, Thursday at SAC,6PM. Do turn up and show lots
of enthu as this is the best chance to be a part of the finest short film
and undergo through a great experience.
P.S: People with already developed scripts are welcomed. All kinds of
genres are encouraged.

Cheers!
